{"tid":1802514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元旦遊行：上次128全香港人都漏左樣好重既野","createTime":"2019-12-29T13:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T14:51:45.000Z","uid":292730,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cb767ab029d37c7b73516088fb064ab4ba5f582c","tid":1802514,"uid":292730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:50:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人。帶遮！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">上次12.8，一百人都無帶一把長遮</span></span><br />\n經過天橋真係個個都大搖大罷無人開遮<br />\n香港人唔好咁懶，冬天就真係唔攞遮<br />\n<br />\n遮已經係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>最基本既抗爭裝備</strong></span></span><br />\n唔知班狗幾時發癲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">局部地區性暴雨時都需要搵把遮擋下鏡頭⋯⋯<br />\n你唔上前線嫌煩都可以留把遮比物資站⋯⋯<br />\n有需要時遮陣已經係幫前線提供最基本既保護⋯⋯<br />\n有不反都好，行過高位保護身邊既手足遮樣已經最基本⋯⋯</span><br />\n<br />\n無長遮都袋把短遮，拜託<br />\n<br />\n最後，P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麻煩推一推<br />\n認同請分享，好人一生平安"},{"pid":"3609ef9275942138e92a6527f11744a8a4463474","tid":1802514,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:53:36.000Z","msg":"簽左99914既入去簽埋呢個德國聯署98731<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1802070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1802070</a>"},{"pid":"5aea40a8c4d07e89a17f63bfb56615b567929e11","tid":1802514,"uid":19933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:54:24.000Z","msg":"1月1日 (三)<br />\n短暫時間有陽光。早上清涼及有一兩陣微雨。<br />\nMin Temperature16&deg;C<br />\nMax Temperature20&deg;C<br />\nHumidity70-90%<br />\n東風4至5級，初時離岸6級。<br />\n短暫時間有陽光。早上清涼及有一兩陣微雨"},{"pid":"51ff40ea5463c726510ae9fc47540a847778c218","tid":1802514,"uid":242323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:00:28.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n要全民帶遮"},{"pid":"defa5c921bde54c8d5597cda924794b819e18891","tid":1802514,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":2,"sc